
Temperature Sensor (DS18B20) Connections

SIG → GPIO4
VCC → 3V3
GND → GND

-----------------------

Ultrasonic Sensor (HR-SR04) Connections

Pin → Connection
VCC → 5V
Trig → GPIO 17
Echo → GPIO 18
GND → GND

-----------------------

Buzzer Module

SIG  → GPIO 27
VCC  → 3.3V (Raspberry Pi)
GND  → GND (Raspberry Pi)